msgstr "11400:Oh, that? Yeah, I'd seen that before.[%p]"

msgid "11500:そしてあのＯ－ＦＲＯＮＴ屋上でも、そんな視点で見てみたら、あった。[%p]"
msgstr "11500:I'd tried to see something like that on top of the O-FRONT building and succeeded.[%p]"

msgid "11600:景色の中に溶け込んでいた、ディソードが。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:I'd seen the Di-Sword blended in with the scenery.[%p]"

msgid "11700:[name]梢[line]「はーい、ピンポンでーす♪」[%p]"
msgstr "11700:[name]梢[line]Yup! That's right![%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃが最初に見えたときは、ハムポンポンが死んじゃったとき」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]梢[line]The first time Kozupii saw it was when Hamponpon died.[%p]"

msgid "11900:ハムポンポン？[%p]"
msgstr "11900:Hamponpon?[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]梢[line]「小学生のとき飼ってたハムスター」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]梢[line]The hamster I had in elementary school.[%p]"

msgid "12100:[name]梢[line]「ほいで、ハムポンポンのお墓を作ってあげよーうって、土手に行ったのら」[%p]"
msgstr "12100:[name]梢[line]I wanted to make a grave for him, so I went out to the riverbank.[%p]"

msgid "12200:[name]梢[line]「でもスコップ忘れて、お墓作れなくて、ふみゅーって泣いていたら」[%p]"
msgstr "12200:[name]梢[line]But I forgot my shovel and I couldn't dig his grave, so I went “Fumyuuh!” and cried a lot.[%p]"

msgid "12300:[name]梢[line]「お空に、この剣の形が見えた」[%p]"
msgstr "12300:[name]梢[line]And then, I saw the shape of the sword in the sky.[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]梢[line]「それからは、いろんなところでよく見るようになったのら」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]梢[line]After that, I started to see it in a lot of places.[%p]"

msgid "12500:どうやって手に入れた？[%p]"
msgstr "12500:How did you get it, though?[%p]"

msgid "12600:僕は結局、ディソードを見つけたものの、つかめなかった。どれだけ手を伸ばしても、手応えはなくて、つかめなかったんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:I'd found it, but I couldn't grab it. No matter how much I reached out, I couldn't touch it or grab it...[%p]"

msgid "12700:[name]梢[line]「ただ、願ったんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "12700:[name]梢[line]I just wished.[%p]"

msgid "12800:願った？[linebreak]手に入れたい、って？[linebreak]でもそれなら僕だって――[%p]"
msgstr "12800:Wished? You wished to get the sword? But I did that, too.[%p]"

msgid "12900:と、こずぴぃは上目遣いで僕を見て、かすかに首を振った。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:Kozupii looked up at me, softly shaking her head.[%p]"

msgid "13000:[name]梢[line]「ちがーうのだ」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]梢[line]Nope.[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]梢[line]「願ったのはね」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]梢[line]My wish...[%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]梢[line]「……殺してやりたい、っていうこと」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]梢[line]was to kill.[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]拓巳[line]「……え？」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "13400:彼女の心の声は、はっきりと僕の頭の中に響く。[linebreak]聞き間違いとかじゃない。[linebreak]今、はっきりと言った。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:I could hear the voice of her mind clearly within my own. I hadn't mistaken it. I'd heard exactly what she said.[%p]"

msgid "13500:“殺してやりたいと願った”って。[linebreak]はにかみながら、言ったんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:“My wish was to kill.” She'd said it with a smile, too.[%p]"

msgid "13600:Ｒｏｆｔの５階から６階へ上る階段には、店内のＢＧＭがかすかに届くくらいで、とても静か。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:The stairs leading up from the fifth floor of the Roft building to its sixth floor were very quiet. You could only faintly hear the music coming from the shops.[%p]"

msgid "13700:僕も、彼女も、一言も発しない。[linebreak]誰かの息づかいが、やけに耳につく。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:She didn't say a word, and neither did I. I could hear somebody's breath loudly in my ears.[%p]"

msgid "13800:それは彼女のもの？[%p]"
msgstr "13800:Was it hers?[%p]"

msgid "13900:いや、僕自身のものだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:No, it was mine.[%p]"

msgid "14000:誰も、来ない階段。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:A staircase where nobody came.[%p]"

msgid "14100:渋谷っていう街の中心にある、死角。エアポケット。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:A blind spot in the dead center of Shibuya. An air pocket.[%p]"

msgid "14200:僕は、渇いたのどを潤すために、唾を飲み込んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I gulped down saliva to wet my suddenly-parched throat.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]梢[line]「そう願いながら、みゅーって空見たら、また剣が見えて」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]梢[line]I wished, and then looked waaaay up into the sky, and I could see the sword.[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]梢[line]「でもでもー、そのときまで、剣とは思ってなかったよ。[linebreak]なんだかガキーンってしたものって思ってた」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]梢[line]But! But! I didn't think it was a sword until then! I just thought it was kind of a big clangy thing.[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]梢[line]「あれでブーン！　ってやったら殺せるかなーって、[linebreak]無意識に手を伸ばしたら……」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]梢[line]I wondered if I could kill them if I went “bang” with it, and I reached out my hand…[%p]"

msgid "14600:[name]梢[line]「ホントに、つかめたのらー」[%p]"
msgstr "14600:[name]梢[line]And I really was able to![%p]"

msgid "14700:それで……どうしたの？[linebreak]なにを、したの？[%p]"
msgstr "14700:And then... what happened? What did you do?[%p]"

msgid "14800:[name]梢[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14800:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14900:[name]梢[line]「殺そうとしたけど、できなかった」[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[name]梢[line]I tried to kill them, but I couldn't.[%p]"

msgid "15000:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃの力じゃ、半殺しにするのが精一杯だったのでーす」[%p]"
msgstr "15000:[name]梢[line]Kozupii wasn't strong enough to do more than half-kill them.[%p]"

msgid "15100:この子は……壊れてる……。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:This girl was... broken.[%p]"

msgid "15200:[name]梢[line]「壊れてなーいよ、ぷんぷん。ここに剣あるもーん」[%p]"
msgstr "15200:[name]梢[line]I'm not broken! Hmph! I've got the sword right here.[%p]"

msgid "15300:彼女が、傍らに置かれたディソードを愛おしそうに見つめるその態度からは、まさに絶対的信頼を置いていることが見て取れた。彼女の心もまた、僕にそう告げていて。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:She was gazing lovingly at the sword next to her. I could tell from the way she was looking at it that she had complete trust in it. Her mind was telling me the same thing.[%p]"

msgid "15400:僕も、これくらい壊れなきゃ、ディソードを手に入れられないのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Maybe I couldn't get the Di-Sword unless I was broken, too.[%p]"

msgid "15500:……そもそも僕は、まだ、壊れてなかったのか？[%p]"
msgstr "15500:Wait, did this mean I wasn't broken already?[%p]"

